issue.body:
@pranavsharma as promised, here are some examples of the experimental C++ API.

**Description**
This PR adds 2 example applications demonstrating the experimental C++ API. They are command line applications that do not require a windows environment to build (unlike the imagenet and MNIST examples). One example is a basic demonstration of using the experimental API and the second example shows how to perform batch processing.

**Motivation and Context**
* Closes https://github.com/microsoft/onnxruntime/issues/4355
* Probably closes https://github.com/microsoft/onnxruntime/issues/3879 for now
* The current examples either require a Windows build environment or are too verbose (in my opinion) to convey the simple usage of the API.
